extendedInfo.description: Pass your DMV permit test and behind the wheel driving test with flying colors. STUDY BY TOPICS: You can study the laws by topic. All questions are sorted by topic. It also tells you the areas that each topic covers. Accidents Alertness Attitude Documents Hazard Awareness Motorway Rules Other Types of Vehicle Road and Traffic Signs Rules of the Road Safety Margins Safety and Your Vehicle Vehicle Handling Vulnerable Road Users HIGHEST QUALITY and QUANTITY: Over 500 questions and 13 topics in all. MOCK TEST MODE: Mock test simulates the real test format. Questions are presented randomly from all the topics. DETAILED TEST RESULTS: A summary of the practice test is presented at the end of each test. It shows you the time you took, the score, which questions you answered correctly and where you were wrong, explanation for all questions. PROGRESS METER With our unique progress tracking feature including pie charts and bar graphs showing your progress, you know you are ready to take on the real test at the board when your progress meter says 100%. FEATURE LIST: â¢ Over 500 multiple-choice questions. â¢ Choose number of questions you would like in each test. â¢ A new module, "Progress Meter" keeps track of how you are performing in a particular topic or mock test. â¢ Special algorithm that randomizes questions every time you take a test. â¢ Mock test has exactly similar format as in real test.Keywords :- permit test,license,driving test,dmv test,california,new york,arizona,texas, DMV prep,test,permit,drivers ed,rules,laws,road,accidents,signs,traffic
